caption.p: The antibacterial activity of A. factorovskyi extract and silver nanoparticles. The antibacterial activities of A. factorovskyi, Tetracycline, AF-AgNPs, and AgNO 3 were tested against different bacterial strains, ( A) the antibiotic diffusion results, ( B) the average inhibition zone in (mm) for the A. factorovskyi ethanolic extract (right), and nanoparticles (Left).
